# BROCHURE-SITE-RULES.md is the master file

All brochure-site conventions live in `BROCHURE-SITE-RULES.md` (same folder).

This `.cursorrules` exists only so Cursor loads the correct instructions
automatically. Do not duplicate rules here — read and follow
`BROCHURE-SITE-RULES.md`.

## For the agent

1. Read `BROCHURE-SITE-RULES.md` first.
2. Follow the kickoff interview in §1 before building anything.
3. Let the client brief decide the page set — do not assume fixed pages.
4. Keep all business facts in one data file; never hardcode them in components.
